messages.content: How should I use the Neutrogena HYDRO BOOST Water Gel Cleanser when cleaning my face?

To effectively use the Neutrogena HYDRO BOOST Water Gel Cleanser, follow these steps:

1.  **Determine Skin Suitability:** Make sure the cleanser is right for your skin type [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==). It's generally good for dry, combination, and sensitive skin [sweetcare](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHYm_FnBNjWUlYYMC92Mom9wp5mcpWIvz8uF3Y_X_dmrteGaIQbOxr-WB4GwPNQpa6AFppaB5e2ADu1anYubxHy8-5_xD0WK3ECIM17DXVGOH9flP7oUJkDwHjx9pl8BwCU4w3CG7x6Z8rH3ENdoSMgXE7JtZQiP9C-NUpDWRKUVLKXTZOa2WcHulD3Hi-RdvFmw0oTU7SkJ9nAqR0=) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==) [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==) [superdrug](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFh4tC7HcemGgTTfbUuajurqD00gTtRGA-G-uSxkbdkMVolgmjrDG9CsVy4qOnD-W-YnjHelDYNzgN9zGpLN2XQYxrjCsfW2BTyp6z9uZQxNMwuuwan2yihnU0hwQ4tXOa_FtSM7q2WVNOzZcjFWu01ZfMA4YsdvQwJmlziFAL37iAGNtCt9CjNePyqjJusow7zVAkmiEHNG4YrxuqnbVojf51aJkWoTK0kzuQ=) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFzXbqzeDW6pgX9XPAt9AcVuT4ZXEKpcCv-XkCpqbJXlTQrnVozuwtsX6wpZqKIjvtwlOYrH86rO_uBprDSyCBgL1Xwb0vcNqXefiJuERBRr4JPfbJnbgu2T69NeDHD7Bgu68WJ5nASzpe6PiFEWBk-7tRuAhLL4saQoFO-xBY=) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJSs8adfA3Y9qS3N6Y9ehndK7a8emGs7QTux6a6D-YFPm7rL8X3-0Sdu4J_tTs-YynoTjGRWBK1b3cZ4axHi08TK_JOPjGgDU-k9rFA74rL8Ow8m5sRl6kf6BXcKbvgCuFg2XBW8m9Kp3rRpQuDkrvnRyvUeQlUax_JtdBSE4zhNQol_PZYn8HFP4xnpYP2IM=). If you have oily or acne-prone skin, this product may also be suitable [trendyol](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgU6hhBws_NX_WKTmNhBjl1atKXYFZy7-H8rpV6u2ng1aPydhCnwU4KxzcJeU71laGBYH2j0SpC60qPUvatcjFubIXb3BcA5NOIhuQqQ4UQj5Bx2ao7cS5-CwjaT8QtzK7glsSWK4MppE4-0opUsdGTyqtJAOTnDSusy424Q710UbL06oIYDCgiJ0DhAqtw2fc9xowNZUdX-4tK0urBCZnlbTpdQOz).
2.  **Pick the Right Time:** You can use this cleanser in the morning and evening as part of your daily skincare [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==) [ulta](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG1Jxd3h4Ys527H2n3TD6MDgQtDJeKjSsTkj64kVllAToQ-b7vZjn3nYZekVHKreKCcudU2dzTxxeZcY-fuzwtmXbuJgf-DoNHp2dnv7xIj0ax2FHQhkADaEkkmyyIk6Q9cixiYCvpmSrIxS6nXxYxiDe7RG-pglEahfBvh1JJu7Nv3OdVKMy5KkA9SARsuQ4eCogl6_r9PPgTSuA==).
3.  **Wet Face:** Start by gently wetting your face with warm water [trendyol](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgU6hhBws_NX_WKTmNhBjl1atKXYFZy7-H8rpV6u2ng1aPydhCnwU4KxzcJeU71laGBYH2j0SpC60qPUvatcjFubIXb3BcA5NOIhuQqQ4UQj5Bx2ao7cS5-CwjaT8QtzK7glsSWK4MppE4-0opUsdGTyqtJAOTnDSusy424Q710UbL06oIYDCgiJ0DhAqtw2fc9xowNZUdX-4tK0urBCZnlbTpdQOz). Remember that the water gel works best on wet or damp skin [reddit](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==1).
4.  **Apply Cleanser:** Put a small amount of the cleanser (about the size of a nut) on your hands [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==) [trendyol](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgU6hhBws_NX_WKTmNhBjl1atKXYFZy7-H8rpV6u2ng1aPydhCnwU4KxzcJeU71laGBYH2j0SpC60qPUvatcjFubIXb3BcA5NOIhuQqQ4UQj5Bx2ao7cS5-CwjaT8QtzK7glsSWK4MppE4-0opUsdGTyqtJAOTnDSusy424Q710UbL06oIYDCgiJ0DhAqtw2fc9xowNZUdX-4tK0urBCZnlbTpdQOz) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJSs8adfA3Y9qS3N6Y9ehndK7a8emGs7QTux6a6D-YFPm7rL8X3-0Sdu4J_tTs-YynoTjGRWBK1b3cZ4axHi08TK_JOPjGgDU-k9rFA74rL8Ow8m5sRl6kf6BXcKbvgCuFg2XBW8m9Kp3rRpQuDkrvnRyvUeQlUax_JtdBSE4zhNQol_PZYn8HFP4xnpYP2IM=].
5.  **Create Lather:** Add water to your hands and rub them together to create a lather [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJSs8adfA3Y9qS3N6Y9ehndK7a8emGs7QTux6a6D-YFPm7rL8X3-0Sdu4J_tTs-YynoTjGRWBK1b3cZ4axHi08TK_JOPjGgDU-k9rFA74rL8Ow8m5sRl6kf6BXcKbvgCuFg2XBW8m9Kp3rRpQuDkrvnRyvUeQlUax_JtdBSE4zhNQol_PZYn8HFP4xnpYP2IM=] [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==) [ulta](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG1Jxd3h4Ys527H2n3TD6MDgQtDJeKjSsTkj64kVllAToQ-b7vZjn3nYZekVHKreKCcudU2dzTxxeZcY-fuzwtmXbuJgf-DoNHp2dnv7xIj0ax2FHQhkADaEkkmyyIk6Q9cixiYCvpmSrIxS6nXxYxiDe7RG-pglEahfBvh1JJu7Nv3OdVKMy5KkA9SARsuQ4eCogl6_r9PPgTSuA==).
6.  **Massage:** Gently massage the lather onto your face and neck using circular motions [trendyol](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgU6hhBws_NX_WKTmNhBjl1atKXYFZy7-H8rpV6u2ng1aPydhCnwU4KxzcJeU71laGBYH2j0SpC60qPUvatcjFubIXb3BcA5NOIhuQqQ4UQj5Bx2ao7cS5-CwjaT8QtzK7glsSWK4MppE4-0opUsdGTyqtJAOTnDSusy424Q710UbL06oIYDCgiJ0DhAqtw2fc9xowNZUdX-4tK0urBCZnlbTpdQOz) [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJSs8adfA3Y9qS3N6Y9ehndK7a8emGs7QTux6a6D-YFPm7rL8X3-0Sdu4J_tTs-YynoTjGRWBK1b3cZ4axHi08TK_JOPjGgDU-k9rFA74rL8Ow8m5sRl6kf6BXcKbvgCuFg2XBW8m9Kp3rRpQuDkrvnRyvUeQlUax_JtdBSE4zhNQol_PZYn8HFP4xnpYP2IM=] [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==).
7.  **Rinse Thoroughly:** Rinse your face well with plenty of water to remove all of the cleanser [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==) [odetobeauty](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGezliSky2_fa8BD9FazPPmbXV5sV03jfMzcSQg7CqybiOnTYrYnZgeSIl7k3oJJ86x2QvDJczYdi2k72x4tk3MSv0rsJksnsMmMAY1CAkdkE7ZV6jaRopgn5OpsyBU0DRlddJ87XcIrwTWqviKJv65c3KYUUmEg1O6WEiG8TNgw8CKBS-3LJx3R9phT7TzauIYVw==) [trendyol](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgU6hhBws_NX_WKTmNhBjl1atKXYFZy7-H8rpV6u2ng1aPydhCnwU4KxzcJeU71laGBYH2j0SpC60qPUvatcjFubIXb3BcA5NOIhuQqQ4UQj5Bx2ao7cS5-CwjaT8QtzK7glsSWK4MppE4-0opUsdGTyqtJAOTnDSusy424Q710UbL06oIYDCgiJ0DhAqtw2fc9xowNZUdX-4tK0urBCZnlbTpdQOz) [neutrogena](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJSs8adfA3Y9qS3N6Y9ehndK7a8emGs7QTux6a6D-YFPm7rL8X3-0Sdu4J_tTs-YynoTjGRWBK1b3cZ4axHi08TK_JOPjGgDU-k9rFA74rL8Ow8m5sRl6kf6BXcKbvgCuFg2XBW8m9Kp3rRpQuDkrvnRyvUeQlUax_JtdBSE4zhNQol_PZYn8HFP4xnpYP2IM=].
8.  **Pat Dry:** Gently pat your face dry with a clean towel [youtube](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==0) [trendyol](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEgU6hhBws_NX_WKTmNhBjl1atKXYFZy7-H8rpV6u2ng1aPydhCnwU4KxzcJeU71laGBYH2j0SpC60qPUvatcjFubIXb3BcA5NOIhuQqQ4UQj5Bx2ao7cS5-CwjaT8QtzK7glsSWK4MppE4-0opUsdGTyqtJAOTnDSusy424Q710UbL06oIYDCgiJ0DhAqtw2fc9xowNZUdX-4tK0urBCZnlbTpdQOz).

If using during the day, apply sun protection after moisturizing [youtube](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8sQEL3FwS_BUYq3JNd4Z6xbB9fHpp-oNhf2uPmmYRxsQ90bOdY-2_AQ7Irzf6Bdzo6I4YTNXrTmbMj1bN6bP4OHypZG2Ss0aXlirNy35hbnlUKJSy028EbbaSGruqKv-R37tSaw0DL23hGyRiVcgKwcNXtYKKYbGEETCK1baQSGgwFOmK7MPsj3YhN1f_xCjjSQ==2).
